Restoring your backups
======================

- Restoring a backup, create a new DB instance
- Retain the parameter group and Security Group
- Changing the storage type will slow down the process.


To restore a snapshot:
======================

    - From snapshots menu option

To restore point in time:
=========================

    -  From the DB Instance or Automated backups
    - Specify point in time to restore them

Why is it too slow to restore?
===============================

    - New volumes are hyderated from S3
    - Blocks are pulled in a needed.
    - Full performance requires the volume to warm up

    - Increase IO for better performance

